sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant W as Web App
    participant X as Wallet
    participant C as Sepolia (Factory + Project)
    participant E as ENS
    participant S as Walrus

    rect rgb(240,248,255)
    Note over U,S: Publish collection (/create)
    U->>W: Upload package / load sample
    W->>E: Validate ENS ownership + resolver access
    W->>C: Check existing projectForCollectionHash
    alt New project
      W->>S: Upload algorithm bundle
      U->>X: Approve deploy
      X->>C: Factory.createProject(...)
      C-->>W: New Project contract
    else Existing project
      W->>C: Read owner + algorithmURI + mintPrice
    end
    U->>X: Approve ENS setup tx(s)
    X->>C: configureEnsSubnames or configureEnsV2Subnames
    W->>E: Write collection text records
    W-->>U: Collection published
    end

    rect rgb(245,255,245)
    Note over U,S: Mint artwork (/collection/[collectionENS])
    U->>W: Open collection
    W->>E: Read collection ENS records
    W->>S: Fetch algorithm bundle
    W->>C: Read nextTokenId + mintPrice + nextArtworkENS
    W->>W: Generate hidden deterministic output
    W->>S: Upload params JSON
    W->>S: Upload rendered PNG
    W->>S: Upload NFT metadata + provenance manifest
    U->>X: Approve mint
    X->>C: Project.mintArtwork(to, metadataURI, uniquenessHash)
    opt ENS subname mode enabled
      C->>E: Create artwork ENS subname
    end
    W->>E: Write artwork ENS text records
    W-->>U: Mint complete + redirect to artwork page
    end
